\f0\b PV_RandWipe.ar(bufferA,  bufferB,  wipe,  trig)\

\f1\b0 \
Cross fades between two sounds by copying bins in a random order.\

\f0\b bufferA
\f1\b0  - fft buffer A.\

\f0\b bufferB
\f1\b0  - fft buffer B.\

\f0\b wipe
\f1\b0  - copies bins from bufferB in a random order as wipe goes from 0 to 1.\

\f0\b trig
\f1\b0  - a trigger selects a new random ordering.\
